    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m so excited to get this absolute beauty into the hands of a new owner. If you\u2019re looking for a car that feels like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in truly flawless shape inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. Seriously, you won't find a single thing out of place. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
