    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is in showroom condition and has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior is flawless, featuring original paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, the switchgear remains crisp to the touch, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new. It comes with a comprehensive, folder-bound service history detailing every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively at authorized service centers. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It is a turn-key investment for a discerning collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
